name: Eclipse
description:
Want me to create custom models for you? please visit my Fiverr page:

https://www.fiverr.com/s/Xar15P

Eclipse

Legal & Risk

In principle, I do not support the use of this model to generate any adult content. When using this model, users must abide by laws and regulations, and do not infringe other people's reputation, privacy or portrait rights.

Changelogs

  • v1.0-Asami: First release, made from self-trained model, merged with various other models

  • v2.0-Byakuren: updated from v1.0, added more hairstyles, more poses, more vehicles, etc, trying to fix hands by using hires trained image.

Who find this model perfect

  • LoRA/LoCon/LyCORIS user who are looking for a compatible checkpoint

  • User who have limited resources, because this checkpoint can generate good image start from 15 sampling steps, no need to wasting time for sampling steps

  • Creative prompters

Usage

  • Almost compatible with all sampling methods available

  • Use 15-40 sampling steps

  • CFG: 4.5-7

  • Less complicated, short negative prompts are better

If using Hires:

  • Hires step: 20 steps or same as sampling steps

  • R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6b, if you're prefer Latent upscaler, use Latent (nearest-exact)

  • Denoising: 0.3-0.7

VAE: https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse-original

After download this model, try to share with us about your findings.

Please give star reviews with your generated picture if you like it.

p.s. It's not necessary but If you like my creations please consider to support me to create more projects by donate in here:

https://ko-fi.com/gorillamonsooniii

I'm also accept commisioning for LoRA etc.
